body:
Okay so

I’ve never seen Killing Eve, but every gif set i see of it gives me one of two impressions of what the show is about:

  1. Two female assassins that are constantly killing each other and being reborn to do it all over again for eternity.
  2. Two lesbian criminals whose kink is sexual tension in the form of threatening each other’s lives, and they’re both switches.

Someonee who knows this show, please tell me if I’m close.
